    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = v0
    tmp = ((wp.cos(v0 + 0.73) / (tmp + 0.84 * v1 + 0.20)) - tmp)
    v1 = wp.exp(wp.sin(tmp))
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.abs(tmp))
    v2 = wp.exp(((v1 + 0.31 / tmp + 0.64) / wp.abs(tmp + 0.21)))
    v2 = v1
    v1 = (((v0 + 0.09 - v0 + 0.11) * 0.89) / v1)
    data[tid] = v0
